<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/25980993">如何优雅地写遗书？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="2575300" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">世上的遗书比真正自杀的人多，听说每个人都想过写遗书。有没有行动，是另一回事。</div>


</div>
